data.description: Welcome to this impressive Colonial boasting over 3,400 square feet on over 2 acres of land! As soon as you walk inside you are met with marble floors in the foyer. To the left you have your formal living room with hardwood floors and plenty of natural light and it also leads to one of the entrances into your den/office! On the right you see the formal dining room perfect for entertaining over the holidays. A little ways in you see the large kitchen with plenty of countertop space, lots of cabinets, a pantry and even a wine fridge! There is also an eat in kitchen space, access to your 2 car garage, first floor laundry and a slider out to your four seasons sun room. The last room on the first floor is the family room with two story ceilings, a wood burning fire place, and lots of room for your furniture. The second floor has an expansive Primary Bedroom suite with ample space, a sitting area, a LARGE walk in closet and a full four piece en suite complete with a soaking jacuzzi. The other 3 bedrooms are generous in size and all have great closet storage. The unfinished basement has high ceilings and offers endless possibilities for storage or future rec room space if you wanted to finished it off! Off the kitchen you walk through your Four Season Sunroom and out to your back yard you get a view of the private, fenced in space, that outdoor deck and patio and also the heated in ground pool! You also notice the built in gas generator incase of any storms that may come!
